Perl (PDL) demos for PLplot
---------------------------

The files in this directory are close translations of the PLplot demos
witten in C (see directory above ../c/).  They use the PDL and
PDL::Graphics::PLplot modules distributed with PDL.

CAVEAT: The scripts in this directory only work with the CVS sources of PDL
(as on 2004-03-01 or later).

